    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature high-revving individual throttle bodies. This example delivers crisp throttle response and linear power delivery through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from recent bushing refreshes and a documented subframe inspection. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, with the VANOS system recently serviced and valves adjusted to factory tolerances. Riding on staggered alloys with high-performance rubber, this M3 offers the quintessential analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
